overview.longBusinessSummary: Venture Global, Inc. engages in the development, construction, and production of natural gas liquefaction and export projects near the U.S. Gulf Coast in Louisiana. It is involved in natural gas transport, shipping, and regasification, as well as sells LNG. Venture Global, Inc. was founded in 2013 and is based in Arlington, Virginia. Venture Global, Inc. is a subsidiary of Venture Global Partners II, LLC.
